<h1>@google/genai Coding Guidelines</h1>
<p>This library is sometimes called:</p>
<ul>
<li>Google Gemini API</li>
<li>Google GenAI API</li>
<li>Google GenAI SDK</li>
<li>Gemini API</li>
<li>@google/genai</li>
</ul>
<p>The Google GenAI SDK can be used to call Gemini models.</p>
<p>Do <em>not</em> use or import the types below from <code>@google/genai</code>; these are deprecated APIs and no longer work.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Incorrect</strong> <code>GoogleGenerativeAI</code></li>
<li><strong>Incorrect</strong> <code>google.generativeai</code></li>
<li><strong>Incorrect</strong> <code>models.create</code></li>
<li><strong>Incorrect</strong> <code>ai.models.create</code></li>
<li><strong>Incorrect</strong> <code>models.getGenerativeModel</code></li>
<li><strong>Incorrect</strong> <code>genAI.getGenerativeModel</code></li>
<li><strong>Incorrect</strong> <code>ai.models.getModel</code></li>
<li><strong>Incorrect</strong> <code>ai.models['model_name']</code></li>
