<hr>
<h2>Extracting Text Output from <code>GenerateContentResponse</code></h2>
<p>When you use <code>ai.models.generateContent</code>, it returns a <code>GenerateContentResponse</code> object.
The simplest and most direct way to get the generated text content is by accessing the <code>.text</code> property on this object.</p>
<h3>Correct Method</h3>
<ul>
<li>The <code>GenerateContentResponse</code> object features a <code>text</code> property (not a method, so do not call <code>text()</code>) that directly returns the string output.</li>
