<h3>Common Mistakes to Avoid</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>Incorrect:</strong> <code>const text = response.text();</code></li>
<li><strong>Incorrect:</strong> <code>const text = response?.response?.text?;</code></li>
<li><strong>Incorrect:</strong> <code>const text = response?.response?.text();</code></li>
<li><strong>Incorrect:</strong> <code>const text = response?.response?.text?.()?.trim();</code></li>
<li><strong>Incorrect:</strong> <code>const json = response.candidates?.[0]?.content?.parts?.[0]?.json;</code></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2>System Instruction and Other Model Configs</h2>
<p>Generate a response with a system instruction and other model configs.</p>
<pre><code class="language-ts">import { GoogleGenAI } from "@google/genai";

const ai = new GoogleGenAI({ apiKey: process.env.API_KEY });
